<subSubSection id="C347651CFFB0F847FF19229BFF04FA00" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE23697FFB0F847FF19229BFE02FA93" blockId="1.[151,1437,978,1437]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FF19229BFEBFFB59" bold="true" box="[199,338,1194,1220]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Comments:</emphasis>
The original publication indicates that the type material of this species is from “Brasilia; ad serra da Lapa un provincial Minas Geraës a 
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB0F847FDFB22FEFD5AFB74" box="[549,695,1231,1257]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">D. Ménétriés</collectorName>
lecta”. The 
<typeStatus id="54E68835FFB0F847FCE122FEFC4BFB74" box="[831,934,1231,1257]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">lectotype</typeStatus>
housed at the 
<collectionCode id="ED4CAE52FFB0F847FB9822FEFB79FB74" box="[1094,1172,1231,1257]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">MZHF</collectionCode>
is labelled as “Brasilia. Min. Geraës” (
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB0F847FEE222C2FE43FA90" box="[316,430,1267,1293]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Ménétriés</collectorName>
leg.).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE23697FFB0F847FF192326FF04FA00" blockId="1.[151,1437,978,1437]" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB0F847FF192326FE63FAAC" author="Rothkirch und Panthen, H. O. H. K. von" box="[199,398,1303,1329]" journalOrPublisher="Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" pagination="589 - 595" part="1912" refId="ref2533" refString="Rothkirch und Panthen, H. O. H. K. von (1912) Neue Sudamerikanische Stigmoderidae, nebst einer Zusammenstellung der mir bekannten Vertreter der Gattungen Conognatha und Pithiscus (Col. Buprest.). Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 1912, 589 - 595. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 48019120508" title="Neue Sudamerikanische Stigmoderidae, nebst einer Zusammenstellung der mir bekannten Vertreter der Gattungen Conognatha und Pithiscus (Col. Buprest.)" type="journal article" year="1912">Rothkirch (1912)</bibRefCitation>
listed 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FE3D2326FC6BFAAF" authority="(Mannerheim)" baseAuthorityName="Mannerheim" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[483,902,1303,1330]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carinata">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FE3D2326FD35FAAD" box="[483,728,1303,1329]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">Conognatha carinata</emphasis>
(Mannerheim)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FC192326FB5FFAAC" authority="(Perty)" baseAuthorityName="Perty" baseAuthorityYear="1830" box="[967,1202,1303,1329]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vulnerata">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FC192326FBB5FAAC" box="[967,1112,1303,1329]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. vulnerata</emphasis>
(Perty)
</taxonomicName>
as synonyms of 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FA5D2326FE68FAC8" authority="(Donovan)" authorityName="Moore &amp; Lander" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Donovan" baseAuthorityYear="1825" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="macleayi">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FA5D2326FF11FAC8" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. macleayi</emphasis>
(Donovan)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FE4A230AFDC9FAC8" baseAuthorityName="Perty" baseAuthorityYear="1830" box="[404,548,1339,1365]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vulnerata">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FE4A230AFDC9FAC8" box="[404,548,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. vulnerata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was revalidated, including 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FCB2230AFC1DFAC9" baseAuthorityName="Mannerheim" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[876,1008,1339,1365]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carinata">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FCB2230AFC1DFAC9" box="[876,1008,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. carinata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as its junior synonym by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB0F847FAF0230AFF08FAE4" author="Hoscheck" firstAuthor="Hoscheck" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" pagination="95 - 289" refId="ref2258" refString="Hoscheck von Muhlhaimb, A. F. von (1934) Monographie der Gattung Conognatha Eschz. Memoires de la Societe Entomologie de Belgique, 24, 95 - 289." type="journal article" year="1934">Hoscheck (1934)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FF2E236EFE96FAE4" baseAuthorityName="Perty" baseAuthorityYear="1830" box="[240,379,1375,1401]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vulnerata">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FF2E236EFE96FAE4" box="[240,379,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. vulnerata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(including its synonym 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FD55236EFCE6FAE5" baseAuthorityName="Mannerheim" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[651,779,1375,1401]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carinata">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FD55236EFCE6FAE5" box="[651,779,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. carinata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) was synonymized under 
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB0F847FBEE236EFB58FAE4" authorityName="Moore &amp; Lander" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Donovan" baseAuthorityYear="1825" box="[1072,1205,1375,1401]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Conognatha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="macleayi">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB0F847FBEE236EFB58FAE4" box="[1072,1205,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="436">C. macleayi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB0F847FB01236EFF08FA00" author="Moore &amp; Lander" firstAuthor="Moore" pageId="1" pageNumber="436" refId="ref2398" refString="Moore, T. &amp; Lander, T. (2010) Revision du genre Conognatha. Collection Systematique. Vol. 24. Tomas Moore &amp; Tieri Lander, Edition Magellanes, 172 pp." type="book" year="2010">Moore &amp; Lander (2010)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
